features: Our cat cage balls are made from all natural silvervine sticks, catnip and gall fruit without any additives. Silvervine, also named Matatabi, grows in wild jungles of southeast Asia. Gall Fruit is dried fruit of silvervine. Catnip is a perennial herb native to Central Asia. What’s more, the cages are 100% hand-woven with no chemical adhesives, thus cat’s health and safety is absolutely assured

Silvervine sticks could effectively help cats foster proper chewing behaviors, and stimulate healthy growth of permanent teeth. It helps cats eliminate dental plague and tartar, get rid of bad breath and improve dental and oral health for your furry friend

Few cats could resist any of these: catnip, silvervine, gall fruit or jingle bell, not to mention the four together! Our cage balls prevail over other toys in terms of attractions. With the temptation of natural plants aroma, it gets lounging cats up and moving with playful exercise, and makes bored and downhearted cats excited. In addition, the cage balls divert your cat’s urge of destructive behaviors
